{"word":"εἰσβιάζομαι","slug":"εἰσβιάζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰσβιάζομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to force one's way into</i>, <el>εἰς οἶκον</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to force oneself into</i> the citizen<i>ship</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}